data.description: WELCOME HOME to your Well-Maintained Multilevel Home situated across the street from GRETNA ELEMENTARY & MIDDLE SCHOOLS!! Open front door to an inviting 19X13 living room. Brand new carpet (w/original wood floors on the whole main level.) complimented w/ fireplace & window seat. Windows are newer with Double Low E-Argon gas-Triple pane w/ lifetime warranty. Around the corner awaits your functional kitchen w/ newer cupboards, backsplash, SS appliances (refrig conveys.) & floor-Sliding glass door opens to the backyard which is fenced & has a small shed, brand new composite deck & 14x14 patio for your entertaining needs. Upstairs holds 3 bedrooms 2 baths. Primary bedroom has 1/2 bath. BONUS features of this charming home are: Attached 1 car garage w/ extra wide driveway-96% efficiency furnace--new electrical box--Ceramic steel siding & low utilities. Small town living within minutes of NEW Gretna Crossing Park (YMCA & Waterpark), the largest HyVee in the world & Nebraska Crossing Outlets.
